                         <font style="background-color: rgb(0, 0, 0);"
                                    color="#00ff00">
                        
                        
                        
                        [root@mydan &nbsp; tools]# &nbsp; ./alarm  &nbsp; 60 &nbsp; ./test.sh<br>
                        
                        
                         <br>
                         </font>
                         </div>
                         
                         
                          <p>
                          <br>
                          参数说明：alarm &nbsp; number-of-seconds &nbsp; command &nbsp; ..<br>
                           &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;    第一个参数是超时秒数<br>
                           &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;    后面是要执行的命令<br>
                    
                           
                           
                           <br><br>
                           当超时时推出并且给启动的命令发送KILL(9)信号<br>
                           
                          </p>

